jdk 21

vendors:
open jdk
oracle jdk
Adoptium jdk

Which JDK to Choose?
OpenJDK: Choose this if you need a free, open-source JDK and are comfortable with community support.
Oracle JDK: Opt for this if you require commercial support, additional tools, and performance optimizations.
Adoptium JDK: Use this if you want a free, open-source JDK with a focus on cross-platform compatibility and reliability.


